text: Henry Weyland (September 9, 1873 - November 11, 1950) was an American gymnast. He competed in four events at the 1904 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1873 births Category:1950 deaths Category:American male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1904 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Joplin, Missouri
